elements.title: antimonumentas in Mexico (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that antimonumentas in Mexico, like those in Guadalajara (pictured), in Morelia, or in Mexico City, are installed by protesters to demand justice for women who suffer from violence in the country?
